{"id":112937,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/10/【组图】“我给大家带礼物了！”——智利矿工营/","date":"2010-10-13T07:39:25Z","modified":"2010-10-14T22:35:22Z","title":"【组图】“我给大家带礼物了！”——智利矿工营救现场","content":"<p><img title=\"智利矿工\" src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2010/10/13/article-1320045-0B97B0CA000005DC-413_634x461.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"智利矿工\" /></p>\n<p><span>第二个获救的矿工Mario Sepulveda</span><span>向人群欢呼</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2010/10/13/article-1320045-0B97B756000005DC-701_634x509.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><span>从地下2000英尺给人们带来了礼物——一袋矿石，他把礼物分发给众人，随后拥抱了他的妻子</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2010/10/13/article-1320045-0B979BE2000005DC-47_634x476.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><span>这是第一个获救的矿工</span><span> Florencio Avalos Silva的微笑</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2010/10/13/article-1320045-0B97AECA000005DC-889_634x424.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><span> Florencio Avalos 的儿子看到爸爸平安后，喜极而泣</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2010/10/13/article-1320045-0B97A0D9000005DC-481_634x372.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><span>Alfonso Avalos, 第一个获救矿工</span><span> Florencio Avalos 的爸爸，和他拥抱</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2010/10/13/article-1320045-0B979B61000005DC-42_634x377.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><span>开心的笑和流泪</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2010/10/13/article-1320045-0B978F1C000005DC-65_634x565.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><span>矿工在井下拥抱救援人员</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2010/10/13/article-1320045-0B97BDFB000005DC-20_634x475.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><span>第三位获救矿工</span><span>Juan Andres Illanes：我已出舱，感觉良好</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://dongxi.net/upload/attached/20101013131042_40835.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><span>救援人员</span><span> Mr Gonzalez 在给矿工们讲解注意事项</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://dongxi.net/upload/attached/20101013131000_20750.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><span> 救援人员</span><span>Manuel Gonzalez在救援舱里的特写</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://dongxi.net/upload/attached/20101013131022_43332.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><span>救援舱即将放入井下</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://dongxi.net/upload/attached/20101013141020_26325.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><span>英雄Gonzalez这时看上去还是有点紧张</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://dongxi.net/upload/attached/20101013141007_34940.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><span>智利总统</span><span>Sebastian Pinera，右数第三个，视察救援舱</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://dongxi.net/upload/attached/20101013141012_93284.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><span>狂喜的智利国民</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2010/10/13/article-1320045-0B9761C1000005DC-822_634x419.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2010/10/13/article-1320045-0B97A5FA000005DC-109_634x428.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><span>开香槟庆祝！</span></p>\n","author":1,"categories":[20534],"tags":[14617,14636,8652]}